description	"Atton Rand

Class: Jedi
Brief Overview: 
A saberist/pistoleer/Force user hybrid class. 

^2Weaponry:
- Heavy Melee
- Lightsaber
-- Yellow style
-- Saber/Blaster Defense (1)
-- Blaster Deflect (1)
-- Saber Throw ^3[CS1]
- Dual Blaster Pistols
-- Based on Clone Pistols (3)
-- 10% less FP damage
- Sonic Grenades (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (2)
- Push (1) ^3[CS2]
- Pull (1) ^3[CS3]
- Absorb (1)
- Protect (2)
- Speed (1)

^8Attributes:
- 50% slower skill cooldown
- Healing (2)
- Force Focus (1)
- Intuition (Passive Force Sense 1)
- Invisible to Force Sense
- BP-free jumps

^3Abilities:
- Poison Darts (3) ^3[CS4*]
^3[*In Melee]

Atton Rand was a pilot native to the planet Alderaan. During the Mandalorian Wars Atton was trained as a Jedi Hunter by Darth Revan, a past which provided him an unorthodox skillset suited to assassination and espionage. He continued to use these skills reluctantly to redeem himself as one of the Lost Jedi who helped Meetra Surik defeat the Sith Triumvirate."